Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: Indiana GOP
email: info@email.in-gop.com
subject: REMINDER! INGOP Election Night Party!
body: You won't want to miss... <> 🚨 REMINDER 🚨 INDIANA GOP ELECTION NIGHT PARTY!Hello, Fellow Republican! This is a reminder that the Indiana GOP invites youto Election Night 2024 at the JW Marriott in Indianapolis on November 5th,2024! Join the Indiana Republican Party and our candidates on election nightto watch the the final results roll in! We will be joined by gubernatorialcandidate Mike Braun, Attorney General Todd Rokita, Lieutenant Governorcandidate Micah Beckwith, congressional candidate Jefferson Shreve, and manymore candidates and elected officials! There is no cost to attend, but toRSVP, please contact: rsvp@indiana.gop . See the flyer below for more details.We will also be auctioning off an extensive collection of fine bourbons onelection night! You can make your bid online using the button below, then joinus for our election night party to make your final bid and pick up your bottleof bourbon! Click Here for the Bourbon Auction!
